OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright or
OL,6,Fsunny evening with the odd shower
OL,7,Faround. Clear spells overnight with
OL,8,Ffurther showers passing through from
OL,9,Fthe west. Becoming breezy over
OL,10,FShetland.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA mixture of bright spells
OL,13,Fand showers, turning heavy and perhaps
OL,14,Fthundery later. Mainly light south-
OL,15,Fwesterly winds but fresh at times over
OL,16,FShetland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
