OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FOvernight showers clearing then a dry,
OL,7,Fbright start Thursday before cloud and
OL,8,Frain spread northeast. Sunshine and
OL,9,Fshowers on Friday and on Saturday
OL,10,Fmorning, becoming drier later. Breezy
OL,11,Fat times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
